							<img class="graphicsServicesCard__img" src="../img/icons/designServicesIcons/servicesDescIcon.webp" alt="" />
							<h3 class="servicesDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--servicesDetails">Website Graphics & Visual Support</h3>
						</div>

						<ul>
							<li>
								<span class="graphicsServicesCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">➤</span>
								<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Custom website UI graphics, logos, icons, banners and CTA elements</span>
							</li>

							<li>
								<span class="graphicsServicesCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">➤</span>
								<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Suitable for new websites, redesigns, and landing pages</span>
							</li>

							<li>
								<span class="graphicsServicesCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">➤</span>
