								<h3 class="servicesDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--servicesDetails">Website UI <br />graphics and icons</h3>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Custom icon sets for website features</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Consistent UI icons for better user experience</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Lightweight illustrations for web pages</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</article>

						<article class="servicesDetailsSection__graphicsSercivesCard graphicsServicesCard">
							<div>
								<img class="graphicsServicesCard__img" src="../img/icons/designServicesIcons/servicesLogoIcon.webp" alt="Schalk van Dyk logo design services icon" />
								<h3 class="servicesDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--servicesDetails">Simple logo <br />design for websites</h3>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Basic logo design for small businesses</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Logo simplification for better web readability</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Web-ready logo formats for websites and apps</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</article>

						<article class="servicesDetailsSection__graphicsSercivesCard graphicsServicesCard">
							<div>
								<img class="graphicsServicesCard__img" src="../img/icons/designServicesIcons/servicesStylingIcon.webp" alt="Schalk van Dyk visual design services icon" />

								<h3 class="servicesDetailsSection__headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--servicesDetails">Visual design <br />improvements</h3>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Background styling (gradients, textures, overlays)</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Colour adjustments for better contrast and branding consistency</span>
								</li>
								<li>
									<span class="graphicsServicesCard__checkmark paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">✔</span>
									<span class="servicesDetailsSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--graphicsServicesCard">Layout visual enhancements for modern UI design</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
