									“Fix or improve a small part <br class="servicesPricingCard__pricingCardSubtitleBreakline" />of my website”
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<span class="servicesPricingCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">➤</span>
								<span class="servicesPricingSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">1–3 small website visuals </span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="servicesPricingCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">➤</span>
								<span class="servicesPricingSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">Simple banner, icons, or logo tweak</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<span class="servicesPricingCard__rightArrow paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">➤</span
								><span class="servicesPricingSection__paragraph paragraph paragraph--servicesPricingCard">Quick design adjustments</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<a class="btn btn--secondary btn--servicesPricingCardGetStarted" href="#getstarted">Get Started</a>
					</article>

					<article class="servicesPricingSection__servicesPricingCard servicesPricingCard">
						<div class="servicesPricingCard__shadowWrapper">
							<div class="servicesPricingCard__headingContainer">
								<h3 class="servicesPricingCard__pricingCardHeading headingH3 headingH3 headingH3--pricingCardHeading">
									Website Visual Pack <br class="servicesPricingCard__pricingCardHeadingBreakline" /><span class="servicesPricingSection__pricingCardByline paragraph--pricingCardByline"
